In Slave Server:
1) Go to : sshd_Config (path: sudo vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config)
2) enable pubkeyAutountication: yes & password: yes
3) Restart sshd by (sudo restart sshd)

IN Master:
1) ssh-keygen # to genarate Pub_key
2) copy Pub_key (sudo cat .ssh/pub_key)

In Slave:
1) ssh-keygen # to genarate Aoutherised-key
2) paste pub_key copyied from Master Server in Aoutherised-ke (sudo cat .ssh/Aoutherised-key)

======================

if you have Slave(user) password you can use copy-ID

ssh-copy-ID username@pubIP

ssh username@pubIP # to check password less conection 

======================




